            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp61",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3614,
            "end": 3676,
            "label": "restatement",
            "text": "As before, this is approximately 13.928, which rounds to 14.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp62",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3676,
            "end": 3710,
            "label": "conclusion",
            "text": "Therefore, the answer is (D) 14.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp63",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3710,
            "end": 3788,
            "label": "reflection",
            "text": "I don't see any errors in this approach, and it confirms the earlier result.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp64",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3788,
            "end": 3878,
            "label": "planning",
            "text": "Alternatively, maybe I can check if plugging in R = 14 satisfies the original condition.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp65",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3878,
            "end": 3903,
            "label": "example",
            "text": "Let R = 14, so A = 14*B\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp66",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3903,
            "end": 3957,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Then, arithmetic mean: (14*B + B)/2 = 15*B/2 = 7.5*B\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp67",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 3957,
            "end": 4012,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Geometric mean: sqrt(14*B * B) = sqrt(14)*B \u2248 3.741*B\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp68",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 4012,
            "end": 4062,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Double the geometric mean: 2 * 3.741*B \u2248 7.482*B\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp69",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 4062,
            "end": 4097,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Compare to arithmetic mean: 7.5*B\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp70",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 4097,
            "end": 4227,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Pretty close, difference is about 7.5 - 7.482 = 0.018*B, which is negligible for the purpose of rounding to the nearest integer.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp71",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 4227,
            "end": 4268,
            "label": "reasoning",
            "text": "Therefore, R = 14 is a suitable answer.\n\n",
            "source": "response"
        },
        {
            "id": "resp72",
            "annotation": true,
            "start": 4268,
            "end": 4301,
            "label": "conclusion",
            "text": "So, the correct option is (D) 14.",
            "source": "response"
        }
